Package arcade.util

Class Box

java.lang.Object
arcade.util.Box
public class Box
extends java.lang.Object
Container that maps a key to a tag category and a series of attributes.

Box objects use two MiniBox objects to map between key, tags, and attributes. Rather than nesting the key to attribute to values, the class automatically joins key and attribute into a new key.

Since:
2.0
Version:
2.3.1
